<plot>A gift from her mother, Mr. Clock wishes eight-year-old Mya a 'good morning' every morning. But since her mother's passing, all Mr. Clock manages to do is remind her of a time that is lost. Sparse with words, Mya turns to her father for consolation, but struggling himself to deal with the loss, it will take another tragedy to help Mya find the right words.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?379589</url></doc>
